Package com.blackrook.small.roles

Interface MIMETypeDriver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultMIMETypeDriver
    public interface MIMETypeDriver
    Describes a MIME-Type driver for Small. A component with this role is used for mapping file extensions to MIME-Types. Small supplies a default implementation of this if a component is not found.
    Author:
    Matthew Tropiano

      • getMIMEType

        String getMIMEType​(String extension)
        Get the corresponding MIME-Type for a file extension. Must resolve case-insensitively.
        Parameters:
        extension - the file extension to look up (extension only, no name separator characters).
        Returns:
        the corresponding type or null if no type found.
